{{version028}}
{{flavour|Summons one or more water elementals.}}

'''Summon Water Elementals''' is a monster-only spell which summons hostile [[water elemental]]s into existence. These elementals are capable of drowning their foes with their attacks, inflicting [[asphyxiation]] damage each turn and effectively [[Silence|silencing]] them. Characters who [[unbreathing|don't need to breathe]] or who can [[amphibious|breathe water]] are immune to this effect.

{{monsters with spell}}

Ilsuiw can sustain at most three elementals summoned by this spell.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
